h2 Variables
p U can setup the variables anyway you like, here's an example
h3 Example of grid-variables.scss:
code
  | $grid-prefix: ''; // Example: set 'grid-' to make wrapper, row and columns grid-*
  | $grid-col-name: 'col';
  | $grid-row-name: 'row';
  | $grid-wrapper-name: 'wrapper';
  | 
  | $grid-columns: 12;
  | $grid-max-width: 65em;
  | $grid-col-padding: 1em;
  | 
  | $grid-breakpoints: (
  |     ('xs', 0px),
  |     ('sm', 768px),
  |     ('md', 992px),
  |     ('lg', 1200px)
  | );
